E 第三个 
选E
D 最后一句话说了
E 错在 用的方法不对 with 后面 
如果好好读最后一句话 就能做对了!!!!



@@@Many cultural anthropologists have come to reject the scientific framework of empiricism that dominated the field until the 1970s and now regard all scientific knowledge as socially constructed. 
反对实验主义(empiricism!!!!! 经验主义框架)1970 之前很流行
现在认为科学是社会的结构

They argue that information about cultures during the empiricist era typically came from anthropologists who brought with them a prepackaged set of conscious and unconscious biases.
经验主义时期的文化信息是来来自有意无意的偏见 
conscious and unconscious biases 有意识无意识的偏见

Cultural anthropology, according to the post-1970s critique, is unavoidably subjective, and the anthropologist should be explicit in acknowledging that fact.
承认这个事实

Anthropology should stop striving to build a better database about cultural behavior and should turn to developing a more humanistic interpretation of cultures. 
The new framework holds that it may be more enlightening to investigate the biases of earlier texts than to continue with empirical methodologies.
研究早期文章的偏见 比 研究经验主义的方法更好
